g.text: With this workflow we create a test image (using cell image generator) simulate a bad camera (kevin's crappy camera), and then
try to perform an analysis and compare it with the original results
The crappy camera can be configured, try
changing the noise and illumination levels,
how 'crappy' can it be and still work
